## Dev Setup

```bash
git clone git@github.com:janakhpon/monocr.git
cd monocr
uv sync --dev
```

### Release Workflow

```bash
uv version --bump patch
uv build
git add .
git commit -m "bump version"
git tag v0.1.17
git push origin main --tags
```

